data.description: Why wait months for new construction? This like new home could be perfect for you! Nestled away in a quiet, and quaint community, with very little maintenance! This up and coming area is great for those looking to stay off of the beaten path and hold solid investments! The home is like new with an open floor plan and privacy between split rooms. This beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts modern counter tops in the kitchen and each bathroom, stainless steel appliances and a separate inside laundry room! The screened in lanai is perfect for early morning or late night relaxing! Make your appointment now!
